### ============================================================
### Currencies V2
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Read endpoints are anonymous.
### Create/Update/Delete require ManagingRole.
### Currency rates are synced by the CurrencyRateSyncTask job (NBP API).
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@admin.com",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

###

# ============================================================
# CURRENCIES
# ============================================================

### Get all currencies — paged (anonymous)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyListVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
###

### Get all currencies — search
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies?searchString=EUR&pageSize=5&pageNo=1
###

### Get currency by id (anonymous)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies/1
###

### Get currency — not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies/99999
###

### Create currency (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 201 Created  →  { "id": <newId> }
# Code must be a valid ISO 4217 code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "EUR",
  "description": "Euro — European Union"
}
###

### Create currency — USD
# Expected: 201 Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "USD",
  "description": "US Dollar"
}
###

### Create currency — invalid ISO code
# Expected: 400 Bad Request  →  validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "XYZ",
  "description": "Not a real currency"
}
###

### Update currency (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 200 OK
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "code": "EUR",
  "description": "Euro — updated description"
}
###

### Delete currency (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

# ============================================================
# CURRENCY RATES (synced from NBP API by the scheduled job)
# ============================================================

### Get latest rate for a currency
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyRateVm { currencyId, rate, date }
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies/1/rate/latest
###

### Get rate for a specific day
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyRateVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies/1/rate?date=2026-03-01
###

### Get rate — currency not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/currencies/99999/rate/latest
###
